@node Additional "MARInA, ©'1998 by Thomas Neidhardt: Additional"

   @{b}MARInA Wizards@{ub}

        ©'98 Thomas Neidhardt, 91058 Erlangen, GERMANY
____________________________________________________________________


@{b}  MARInA Future @{ub}

    * A new module: The Types-Converter (already in work)
      With it, you may drop a file upon the dock, and will be
      presented with a selectable list depending on the file's
      format (Audio, Gfx, Text, ...). Choose the format which
      you want the file to be converted to, double-click,
      ready, go! MARInA.

    * supply a more transparent BackupManager-Configuration

    * ... same for the ManualServer-Config

    * Create a separate and thus smaller User-RefTable
      for User-Access only.

    * build-in speech recognition as soon as appropriate hard-
      and softwrae are available.

    * perhaps integrate into a newer interface

    * make things run quicker

    * build-in user-hotline requests

    * fix unknown bugs



@{b}  What we still need is to modernize the ReqTools Package, so that@{ub}

    * the ReqTools-Requesters support Drag'n Drop
      of Files out of the Requester
      such as WB-Objects.

    * it is possible to rename Files inside the FileRequester's
      ListViews.

    * the ListViews allow to sort the contents
      by Name, Date or FileType.

    * the rt-Requesters are enhanced by Radio-Button-Requesters

    * the rt-Requesters are enhanced by Checkmark-Requesters

____________________________________________________________________
@endnode



